{"tid":1544851,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"太子事件推理","createTime":"2019-09-05T16:47:54.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-06T02:35:39.000Z","uid":190895,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"438a3dfa6604bf4f156bf283e712e7b8aac1da64","tid":1544851,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:47:54.000Z","msg":"831事件好似中間果層片段比較少,總之有一層係比較少。我自己推理係果層既人曾經反抗過 一齊打番班狗 所以班狗先會更加狠打番手足 導致打死唔止一個手足<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n最後有班手足爆門行路軌走 有另外手足幫手頂住班狗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 所以班狗就打死左佢地......<br />\n<br />\n我睇完蘋果段野推理番黎 因為行路軌果個手足話試過焗住打 打到周圍都血......<br />\n<br />\n大家不如討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f0211e773609dfc4b789570795112af55473a3cb","tid":1544851,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:48:25.000Z","msg":"自推0/10"},{"pid":"bdfa508b0b066fde27fd7c8a51c8fef0198badbf","tid":1544851,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:48:35.000Z","msg":"自推1/10"},{"pid":"add43555eae380db45a0b71aa82b5dcfa962eeb8","tid":1544851,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:48:46.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"a6fd0c51181b6134b3a13e006e2a223ba59972c5","tid":1544851,"uid":190895,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:00.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"c68cf3205868ecccc234735ff2fa1f6486ca25e0","tid":1544851,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-05T16:49:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">[ 極緊急！！ ]<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore